3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a protocol for monitoring player fatigue, which involves control systems and algorithms. 
4. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper discusses the use of WBASN for monitoring player fatigue in the context of sports, which involves human-computer interaction.
